-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Image to Base64</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Convert images to Base64 online for free. Encode JPG, PNG or WEBP images into Base64 text instantly.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/favicon-generator\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Favicon Generator</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Create website favicons from JPG, PNG or WEBP images online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/image-to-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Image to PDF</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Convert JPG, PNG or WEBP images to PDF online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/watermark-image\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Watermark Image</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Add text watermark to images online for free. Protect JPG, PNG and WEBP images instantly.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/flip-image\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Flip Image</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Flip images horizontally or vertically online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/pdf-to-image\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF to Image</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Convert PDF pages to PNG images online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/pdf-merge\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Merge</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Merge multiple PDF files into one PDF online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/pdf-split\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Split</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Split a PDF by page ranges or selected pages online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/compress-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Compress PDF</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Compress PDF pages as optimized images online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/extract-pdf-pages\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Extract Pages</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Extract selected PDF pages into a new PDF online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/rotate-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Rotate</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Rotate all PDF pages 90, 180 or 270 degrees online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/delete-pdf-pages\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Delete Pages</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Delete selected pages from a PDF and download the remaining pages.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/grayscale-image\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Grayscale Image</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Convert JPG, PNG or WEBP images to grayscale online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/watermark-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">PDF Watermark</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Add a text watermark to every PDF page online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/add-page-numbers-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Add Page Numbers to PDF</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Add page numbers to each PDF page online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/organize-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Organize PDF</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Reorder and remove PDF pages online, then download an organized PDF.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/crop-pdf\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">PDF Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Crop PDF</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Crop PDF page margins online by adjusting page crop boxes in your browser.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/meme-generator\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Image Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Meme Generator</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Create a classic meme image with top and bottom text online for free.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/video-metadata\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Video Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Video Metadata Viewer</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">View MP4, WEBM and MOV metadata including duration, file size and resolution.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/audio-metadata\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Audio Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Audio Metadata Viewer</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">View MP3, WAV, OGG and M4A metadata including duration and file size.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/mp4-to-mp3\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Video Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Extract Audio from MP4</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Extract audio from MP4 video in your browser and download it as WAV.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/mp3-cutter\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Audio Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">MP3 Cutter</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Trim MP3 audio by start and end time in your browser and export WAV.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/change-audio-volume\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Audio Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Change Audio Volume</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Adjust MP3, WAV, OGG or M4A volume in your browser and export WAV audio.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/video-to-gif\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Video Tools</div><h2 class=\"mb-2 text-2xl font-bold\">Video to Animated WebM</h2><p class=\"text-slate-400\">Create a short animated WebM preview from MP4 or WEBM video without claiming GIF output.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-slate-900/70 p-6\" href=\"/convert/compress-video\"><div class=\"mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400\">Video Tools</div><h2 cla